                <h1>Explore the Rich History of Cracker Barrel</h1>
                <p>Cracker Barrel was founded in 1969 by Dan Evins in Lebanon, Tennessee. Originally a gas station, it transformed into a family-friendly restaurant and gift shop, featuring Southern comfort food and country-themed décor. Known for its rustic charm, Cracker Barrel emphasizes a nostalgic experience that celebrates Americana, making it a beloved dining destination.</p>
